query:
SELECT 
  qp.questionId, 
  qp.userId,
  qp.firstAttemptStatus,
  qp.lastAttemptCorrect,
  qp.attemptCount,
  q.topicId
FROM question_progress qp
JOIN questions q ON qp.questionId = q.id
JOIN topics t ON q.topicId = t.id
WHERE t.courseId = 2
AND qp.userId = (SELECT id FROM users WHERE email = 'testyou@me.com')
LIMIT 20;
